WHY THIS LICENSE
This pipeline is built on the HEST `register_dapi_he` recipe and the HEST-1k
resource (Mahmood Lab), which are released under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0. To respect
those upstream terms, this repository adopts the same license. As a result,
DOWNSTREAM AND COMMERCIAL USE IS CONSTRAINED BY THE UPSTREAM (HEST) TERMS:
non-commercial use only, with share-alike. If you need commercial terms, you
must obtain them from the upstream authors; this license cannot grant them.

VALIS (Gatenbee et al.) and StarDist (Schmidt et al.) carry their own licenses;
consult those projects for their terms. See CITATION.cff and the README Credits
section for citations.

